  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Taurolidine alone or in combination with citrate have been proposed for locking the catheter
      to reduce the number of catheter infections. As there is not enough evidence to give
      recommendations in this regard, the study tested the hipothesis that taurolidine improves the
      outcome of long term paretneral nutrition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
